{"tid":720691,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"係唔係我對同事既要求太高？","createTime":"2018-06-28T06:14:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-01T02:56:47.000Z","uid":101558,"like":484,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"14a6cd41ddd13c7deecd7ee5b3843e297bcd6720","tid":720691,"uid":101558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T06:14:04.000Z","msg":"話說返工就每人一部電腦（除左我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n我最底級所以無電腦既<br />\n做左一個月到<br />\n同同事都相處幾好<br />\n有次我電話無電<br />\n咁啱得其中一個同事有iPhone 線插係電腦到<br />\n但無插住電話<br />\n咁就問佢<br />\n我：唔好意思，我電話無電，可唔可以借條線比我差一差電？<br />\n同事：唔得，點解我要借比你<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n心諗，驚公司要比多啲電費定點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔明點解會咁寸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：平時都有一齊吹下水既同事嚟"},{"pid":"5cda3dcf53b76801722693ec0e38b91d238475c8","tid":720691,"uid":176063,"like":281,"dislike":1,"score":280,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T06:15:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1af348cc299d9191723ac34750e0b827320e3358","tid":720691,"uid":101558,"like":4,"dislike":57,"score":-53,"quote":{"pid":"5cda3dcf53b76801722693ec0e38b91d238475c8","tid":720691,"uid":176063,"like":281,"dislike":1,"score":280,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T06:15:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T06:17:00.000Z","msg":"女條嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce43e85fff8d7f10dd681a9a43f89f06e7536619","tid":720691,"uid":101558,"like":3,"di